WEBVTT

01:15.333 --> 01:16.876
Hello. Am I on time?

01:16.877 --> 01:19.099
ID, please.

01:20.630 --> 01:23.674
Let me ask you,
my ticket was paid by a company,

01:23.675 --> 01:26.621
can I get the miles?

01:26.970 --> 01:30.222
No, there are no miles for this fare.

01:30.223 --> 01:33.170
l see. Never mind, then.

01:33.268 --> 01:35.852
Boarding is through gate 3.

01:36.146 --> 01:37.437
Thanks.

02:01.087 --> 02:02.171
I´ll help you.

02:02.172 --> 02:03.350
Fine.

02:35.705 --> 02:37.566
Business or pleasure?

02:38.375 --> 02:40.545
Both, I hope.

02:42.504 --> 02:43.682
What do you do?

02:44.798 --> 02:46.400
l´m a model.

02:48.593 --> 02:50.719
Sorry, I should have figured.

02:50.720 --> 02:52.115
Thank you.

02:53.390 --> 02:54.974
Catwalk or advertising?

02:54.975 --> 02:56.421
Catwalk.

03:01.147 --> 03:03.691
And you, what do you do sir?

03:03.692 --> 03:05.734
- You´re killing me.
- Why?

03:05.735 --> 03:06.735
You said ´´sir´´

03:06.736 --> 03:10.821
and I sank
to the fifth circle of hell.

03:10.865 --> 03:14.225
l have to do something
about my hair.

03:15.286 --> 03:19.061
l´m a music critic.
Sounds horrible, I know.

03:19.582 --> 03:22.334
It doesn´t.
Rock?

03:22.335 --> 03:24.558
Now you´re trying to be nice.

03:25.338 --> 03:26.785
Classical music.

03:28.425 --> 03:29.675
I see.

03:29.676 --> 03:32.219
My first boyfriend
was a classical musician.

03:32.220 --> 03:34.972
Well, that´s what he studied.

03:34.973 --> 03:36.098
What´s his name?

03:36.099 --> 03:38.684
No, he´s not famous.

03:38.685 --> 03:42.604
He sent in some works
back when we were together,

03:42.605 --> 03:45.448
but they were never published.

03:45.483 --> 03:48.527
Or printed.
What´s the right word?

03:48.528 --> 03:53.428
Choose whatever term you like
and l´ll make it popular.

03:55.160 --> 03:58.468
Pasternak. Gabriel Pasternak.

04:03.668 --> 04:05.684
Pasternak...

04:08.256 --> 04:12.217
lf I´d known it, l´d have told you
I was a gravedigger, not a critic.

04:12.218 --> 04:15.596
He submitted his thesis
at the Conservatory of Music

04:15.597 --> 04:19.099
when I was president of the jury.
l ripped him apart.

04:19.100 --> 04:21.101
Yes, I was with him at the time.

04:21.102 --> 04:22.770
What you did to him was awful.

04:22.771 --> 04:25.689
He spent a week in bed
after reading the review.

04:25.690 --> 04:29.026
Sometimes I have to destroy
some poor guy´s self-esteem

04:29.027 --> 04:31.820
to protect the ears
of an entire population.

04:31.821 --> 04:35.074
I may be wrong sometimes,
but in this case...

04:35.075 --> 04:37.504
His work was...

04:38.369 --> 04:41.679
a dreadful monstrosity.

04:41.748 --> 04:43.749
Are you still in touch with him?

04:43.750 --> 04:46.043
We didn´t end on great terms.

04:46.044 --> 04:48.879
But l´m still fond of him.
He was a good guy.

04:48.880 --> 04:53.008
Maybe, but if you present
a piece like that to a jury

04:53.009 --> 04:55.761
there has to be
something wrong with you.

04:55.762 --> 04:58.680
Gabriel Pasternak!
How could I forget him?

04:58.681 --> 05:01.266
We laughed about it for months.

05:01.267 --> 05:06.167
l´m sorry to interrupt,
but I was listening to you.

05:06.523 --> 05:08.693
What a huge coincidence!

05:08.858 --> 05:11.443
Gabriel Pasternak
was my student

05:11.444 --> 05:13.667
at Palomar Elementary School.

05:14.989 --> 05:19.743
I had to tell him
he was being held back.

05:19.744 --> 05:23.455
I can assure you:
the kid had issues.

05:23.456 --> 05:26.542
l´ve never seen anything like it
in 30 years as a teacher.

05:26.543 --> 05:28.168
He was screaming

05:28.169 --> 05:31.380
and crying like a newborn baby.

05:31.381 --> 05:33.500
Miss Leguizamón?

05:34.217 --> 05:36.233
lgnacio Fontana.
Remember me?

05:37.053 --> 05:39.689
lgnacio Fontana!

05:39.848 --> 05:43.642
Unbelievable!
There´s a cosmic connection here.

05:43.643 --> 05:47.521
Wasn´t Pasternak one of your classmates?

05:47.522 --> 05:51.024
- Are you friends with him?
- Intimate friends.

05:51.025 --> 05:53.902
Poor guy, we were awful to him.

05:53.903 --> 05:56.446
This is beyond unbelievable.

05:56.447 --> 05:58.448
I was a manager at Home Depot,

05:58.449 --> 06:01.827
where this psycho you mentioned
worked for a while.

06:01.828 --> 06:05.455
He always had trouble with customers,
so we had to let him go.

06:05.456 --> 06:06.903
- And when I...
- Excuse me.

06:07.917 --> 06:11.128
Does anyone else know Gabriel Pasternak?

06:11.129 --> 06:12.588
- Me.
- Me too.

06:12.589 --> 06:13.767
Why?

06:15.008 --> 06:16.842
Why are you on this plane?

06:16.843 --> 06:18.962
Did you buy your tickets?

06:19.512 --> 06:23.390
l´m in real estate,
they sent it to me to check out a farm.

06:23.391 --> 06:26.018
I have a meeting
with the Tourism Secretary.

06:26.019 --> 06:27.827
They bought the ticket.

06:27.979 --> 06:29.313
l won mine in a raffle.

06:29.314 --> 06:34.214
I couldn´t change the date.
l had to fly today.

06:40.992 --> 06:44.559
Gabriel Pasternak is
the cabin chief on this flight.

06:45.330 --> 06:47.998
We did our training together,
we were friends.

06:47.999 --> 06:51.168
Then he asked me out
and when I refused, he started to get...

06:51.169 --> 06:52.461
Never mind.

06:52.837 --> 06:55.839
After takeoff,
he brought coffee to the cockpit.

06:55.840 --> 06:58.425
The door is locked,
the pilots won´t answer,

06:58.426 --> 07:01.269
I´m desperate!
I don´t know what to do!

07:06.184 --> 07:09.130
I cheated on him
with his only friend.

07:10.355 --> 07:11.801
With him!

07:24.702 --> 07:27.537
Gabriel!
Gabriel, are you there?

07:27.538 --> 07:28.455
It´s Victor,

07:28.456 --> 07:29.915
Victor Jensen!

07:29.916 --> 07:31.416
Talk to me, please!

07:31.417 --> 07:34.378
- Who are you?
- I was his psychiatrist for years.

07:34.379 --> 07:38.090
Then I raised my fees,
he got mad and stopped seeing me.

07:38.091 --> 07:39.633
Open the door, Gabriel!
Listen!

07:39.634 --> 07:43.762
It´s not your fault!
You´re just a victim here!

07:43.763 --> 07:45.681
l´m telling you, plain and simple:

07:45.682 --> 07:48.433
it was your parents
who ruined your life!

07:48.434 --> 07:51.137
They asked too much of you
ever since you were born,

07:51.187 --> 07:54.340
they projected all their
disappointments on you!

07:54.357 --> 07:56.817
They are responsible
for your suffering!

07:56.818 --> 07:59.402
Gabriel, no one here...

07:59.445 --> 08:01.616
has anything to do with it!

09:22.195 --> 09:27.095
WlLD TALES

10:54.454 --> 10:56.469
Good evening.
Party of one?

10:56.539 --> 10:59.434
l see you´re good at math.

10:59.792 --> 11:01.084
One, yes.

11:02.378 --> 11:03.877
Wherever you like.

11:16.559 --> 11:19.102
Today´s special
is lentils and rice stew.

11:19.103 --> 11:20.653
Delicious!

11:43.794 --> 11:45.500
Did he order?

11:49.759 --> 11:53.532
That guy´s from my hometown.

11:53.763 --> 11:57.898
He´s a loan shark, a gangster.

11:58.684 --> 12:01.527
He auctioned our house.

12:01.562 --> 12:05.492
Because of him,
my father killed himself.

12:06.817 --> 12:09.972
Two weeks after the funeral,

12:10.321 --> 12:13.112
he tried to seduce my mom.

12:14.283 --> 12:19.040
He wouldn´t leave her alone
so we moved here.

12:20.873 --> 12:22.541
You know how many times

12:22.542 --> 12:25.281
l dreamed of having him

12:25.753 --> 12:27.872
right in front of me?

12:29.048 --> 12:31.736
I´m going to say something.

12:32.385 --> 12:34.090
Say something?

12:34.845 --> 12:37.097
Your dad kills himself
because of this guy,

12:37.098 --> 12:40.096
and you´re just going
to insult him?

12:40.851 --> 12:44.730
Let´s put rat poison in his food.

12:45.940 --> 12:47.482
There´s some in the storeroom.

12:47.483 --> 12:51.930
A good dose and his heart
will blow in five minutes.

13:02.623 --> 13:04.639
Lots of work?

13:04.834 --> 13:06.626
Not with this weather...

13:06.627 --> 13:09.588
I´ve been trying to get your attention
for a while.

13:09.589 --> 13:11.966
You need to check on
your customers, honey.

13:13.134 --> 13:15.510
Sorry.
Can I take your order?

13:15.511 --> 13:17.554
French fries with fried eggs.

13:17.555 --> 13:20.294
I´ll order something else
if I´m still hungry.

13:23.769 --> 13:26.104
- To drink?
- Diet Coke.

13:26.105 --> 13:27.604
Diet Coke?

13:27.898 --> 13:30.275
Diet Coke.

13:30.276 --> 13:32.360
French fries, fried eggs.

13:32.361 --> 13:34.429
Want me to write it?

13:37.950 --> 13:40.431
I hate him!

13:44.707 --> 13:47.757
Make him French fries with fried eggs.

13:50.129 --> 13:53.696
Are you crazy?
Want me to go to prison?

13:54.050 --> 13:55.548
To prison?

13:56.385 --> 14:00.212
Who´ll do the autopsy on this jerk?
The FBl?

14:00.640 --> 14:02.390
French fries with fried eggs.

14:02.391 --> 14:04.976
They´ll think the cholesterol
killed him.

14:09.273 --> 14:11.754
Just cook his meal, will you?

14:21.202 --> 14:23.244
Can I have your opinion?

14:23.245 --> 14:26.710
You seem like a smart girl.
Come here.

14:29.627 --> 14:32.832
Which do you like better? This one?

14:33.172 --> 14:35.173
CUENCA = SAFETY

14:35.174 --> 14:36.724
Or this one?

14:37.051 --> 14:38.176
The red one.

14:38.177 --> 14:40.244
The red one.
Hold on.

14:43.182 --> 14:45.141
Don´t I look too serious?

14:45.142 --> 14:46.810
No, I think it´s fine.

14:46.811 --> 14:48.361
Thank you.

14:54.318 --> 14:56.861
Besides, prison´s not that bad.

14:56.862 --> 14:59.155
It just has bad reputation.

14:59.156 --> 15:03.118
They feed you, you don´t pay rent,

15:03.119 --> 15:05.537
you have nothing to worry about.

15:05.538 --> 15:09.124
And if you make nice friends,
you can have a good time.

15:09.125 --> 15:11.347
You play cards...

15:11.460 --> 15:13.545
Were you in prison?

15:13.546 --> 15:14.724
A while.

15:15.423 --> 15:18.783
And I felt freer in there than here.

15:18.968 --> 15:20.311
This is shit.

15:20.845 --> 15:22.705
What did you do?

15:23.013 --> 15:25.184
Nothing I regret.

15:29.854 --> 15:32.397
And he´s running for mayor!

15:32.398 --> 15:34.827
That son of a bitch.
Can you believe it?

15:35.234 --> 15:38.695
Of course I can.
Bastards rule the world.

15:38.696 --> 15:40.246
Wake up, kid!

15:42.658 --> 15:43.898
So?

15:44.493 --> 15:47.491
Shall we do the community a favor?

15:52.460 --> 15:53.751
Great!

16:20.488 --> 16:21.934
You did it.

16:23.157 --> 16:26.910
Don´t play naive,
as if you hadn´t noticed.

16:26.911 --> 16:28.357
What?

16:29.872 --> 16:31.080
That´s our country.

16:31.081 --> 16:33.875
Everyone wants these guys
to get what they deserve,

16:33.876 --> 16:37.128
but no one
is willing to lift a finger.

16:37.129 --> 16:39.145
Be proud, kid.

16:39.840 --> 16:44.135
For once in your miserable life,
you´re doing something worthwhile.

16:44.136 --> 16:46.971
- I´m not doing anything.
- You´re not?

16:46.972 --> 16:50.225
You stay here arguing instead of
taking the food away from him.

16:50.226 --> 16:51.828
Relax.

16:51.894 --> 16:53.858
You have nothing to worry about.

16:54.230 --> 16:58.024
If there´s an investigation,
I´ll say I used rat poison in the kitchen

16:58.025 --> 17:01.528
because we were infested,
which is true, by the way,

17:01.529 --> 17:04.030
and some of it,
accidentally fell into a pot.

17:04.031 --> 17:05.840
What will they say?

17:08.202 --> 17:09.907
This is insane.

17:13.499 --> 17:15.566
Could this shit be expired?

17:21.674 --> 17:23.793
There´s no expiration date.

17:23.843 --> 17:25.301
How does it work?

17:25.302 --> 17:30.202
If rat poison is expired,
is it more or less harmful?

17:48.909 --> 17:50.702
- Everything OK?
- Yes.

17:50.703 --> 17:51.994
Have a seat.

18:06.302 --> 18:10.075
- What are you having, Alexis?
- Fanta, maybe?

18:10.264 --> 18:12.724
- Should I warm it up?
- No! Leave it.

18:12.725 --> 18:15.351
lf I need you to warm it up, l´ll ask.

18:15.352 --> 18:17.471
Can I have a Fanta, please?

18:21.984 --> 18:24.051
I´ve had it with this girl.

18:30.200 --> 18:32.118
We have to do something,
they´re both eating.

18:32.119 --> 18:34.370
- Add more poison?
- He´s just a kid!

18:34.371 --> 18:37.123
But he´ll grow up.
Like father, like son.

18:37.124 --> 18:40.277
We´d better wipe out
the whole family tree.

18:43.589 --> 18:46.018
l´m feeling a bit...

18:47.134 --> 18:48.312
What´s wrong?

18:51.055 --> 18:51.930
Are you OK?

18:51.931 --> 18:53.264
This must be freezing cold.

18:53.265 --> 18:55.022
No, stop!

18:55.309 --> 18:58.772
Who the fuck taught you
how to wait tables? Leave.

19:12.493 --> 19:15.995
You goddamned fucking bitch!

19:15.996 --> 19:17.413
Stop it, dad!

19:17.414 --> 19:18.957
Pick everything up.

19:18.958 --> 19:20.404
Pick it up, I said.

19:21.710 --> 19:23.211
Call an ambulance!

19:23.212 --> 19:25.383
Pick them up, one by one!

19:25.923 --> 19:27.266
Take this!

19:28.133 --> 19:30.551
Take this, you thug!

19:30.552 --> 19:34.224
I´ll gut you like a chicken!

21:44.186 --> 21:46.305
Come on, moron, move over.

21:55.572 --> 21:57.640
What´s your problem?

22:04.748 --> 22:07.643
What a piece of shit!

22:18.220 --> 22:20.442
You motherfucking redneck!

22:21.473 --> 22:22.765
Asshole!

22:32.860 --> 22:35.392
Holy Jesus.

23:01.305 --> 23:03.165
l can´t believe it.

24:45.742 --> 24:46.909
Hello.

24:46.910 --> 24:51.810
I´m at Kilometer 60
on the route between Salta and...

24:52.749 --> 24:53.916
Yes, sorry.

24:53.917 --> 24:57.277
UlA719.

24:57.379 --> 24:59.343
Diego Iturralde.

25:00.424 --> 25:01.612
Fine.

25:02.467 --> 25:05.344
I was saying, I have a flat tire,
at Kilometer 60

25:05.345 --> 25:10.245
on the route between
Salta and Cafayate.

25:10.934 --> 25:14.228
I´d like to know,
how quick can you get here?

25:14.229 --> 25:18.883
See, the car´s new
and I´m not handy with the jack.

26:32.974 --> 26:34.318
What´s wrong?

26:34.559 --> 26:36.394
Did you get scared?

26:36.395 --> 26:37.686
Come on, man, drive on.

26:38.855 --> 26:40.768
Keep driving, come on!

27:11.263 --> 27:14.140
Let it go, I don´t want a fight.

27:14.141 --> 27:17.017
If I offended you, I apologize.

27:17.018 --> 27:19.189
l´m sorry if I did.

27:25.735 --> 27:27.234
Are you done?

27:27.904 --> 27:29.403
Are you finished?

27:30.907 --> 27:32.406
Careful with...

27:36.830 --> 27:38.897
