but I don´t think it´s necessary.

28:37.891 --> 28:39.069
Fuck!

28:39.267 --> 28:40.445
Stop!

28:45.106 --> 28:46.774
Good morning, officer.

28:46.775 --> 28:48.567
I´m at Kilometer 60

28:48.568 --> 28:50.903
of the route
between Salta and Cafayate

28:50.904 --> 28:53.281
