30:25.248 --> 30:26.850
Pussy!

31:06.665 --> 31:07.843
What are you doing?

31:11.378 --> 31:12.721
Stop, you prick!

32:25.910 --> 32:27.995
You´re dead!

32:27.996 --> 32:30.382
I have your license plate,
you son of a bitch!

32:30.415 --> 32:31.582
Did you hear me?

32:31.583 --> 32:34.168
