41:03.970 --> 41:05.572
There, please.

41:06.514 --> 41:07.805
Sign.

41:11.018 --> 41:12.413
Yes, honey?

41:13.312 --> 41:18.212
I´ll stop by the office, make a few calls
and be on my way.

41:18.401 --> 41:21.606
l´ll be there at 5 with the cake.

41:21.862 --> 41:26.051
I´ll be there on time, don´t worry.

41:43.759 --> 41:46.137
I hope she likes it.

41:46.554 --> 41:47.721
Yes, she´ll love it.

41:47.722 --> 41:49.065
Thank you.

42:03.112 --> 42:04.921
