43:42.294 --> 43:44.629
- I don´t like that tone.
- I´m being polite, sir.

43:44.630 --> 43:45.973
l don´t think so.

43:48.384 --> 43:50.343
The towing fee is 490 pesos

43:50.344 --> 43:53.138
and the parking ticket
will be sent to your address.

43:53.139 --> 43:56.182
